                </p>
                <h1 class="c-heading--article-page u-text-center u-margin-bottom-xs u-text-weight-light">性別多樣性：廣納人才</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="l-grid__row">
            <div class="l-grid__column-medium-10 offset-medium-1 u-margin-bottom-m editorial-header">
                    <figure class="c-image u-margin-bottom-m ">
                        <img src="/-/media/allianzgi/globalagi/editorial/gender-diversity/gender-diversity-hero.jpg?rev=-1&amp;h=1230&amp;w=1920&amp;la=zh-TW&amp;hash=6E32F788A4DF720432B9B4A59E13061A" class="c-image__img" alt="" />
                    </figure>

                
